methods.apply:
Apply this function to the input chunk, returning an output chunk.

 The result is owned by this Context.

:param input: io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Chunk<ToLongCast.T>
:return: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.LongChunk<ToLongCast.T>) the result LongChunk
methods.makeToLongCast:
Create an LongFunctor that casts the values in an input chunk to an long.  An optional offset is applied to each
 value after the cast.

Note: Java generics information - <T extends io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.Any>

:param type: io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.ChunkType
:param size: int
:param offset: long
:return: (io.deephaven.db.v2.hashing.ToLongFunctor<T>) a ToLongFunctor that can be applied to chunks of type in order to produce an LongChunk of values
